name: sdk/google/drive/Create spreadsheet

24d1302f-1e73-4840-b148-64249d7df2ec.name: session Id
24d1302f-1e73-4840-b148-64249d7df2ec.description:
Receives the session id of the drive action.

Example: 
"drive_session"

75f0a459-5fd3-4e11-9a8e-ed53837bf815.name: file meta data

1e44bf09-0522-4a43-b524-3c6fab130d55.name: supports all drives
1e44bf09-0522-4a43-b524-3c6fab130d55.description:
Receives `supportsAllDrives` parameter whether create should support both drives and shared drives.

Example: 
"true"

2a92df1e-487e-4a8f-ae6b-d67b78865f3f.name: done

aea1df37-cfaf-4e6f-84e8-feb357ee766c.name: error

description:
Creates new spreadsheet on the given shared folder.

Example:
1. `session Id` receives "drive_session"@0 
2. `file meta data` receives  {
  "name": "Test from CRANQ dynamic",
  "parents": [
    "FOLDER_ID"
  ]
}@0
3. `supports all drives` receives false@0
4. `done` sends {"fileid": "1_ewweewweFileID"}@0
